================================================================================
MODEL LICENSES AND USAGE RESTRICTIONS
================================================================================

IMPORTANT: This software downloads and uses pre-trained AI models that may have
their own licensing terms and usage restrictions:

1. OpenAI Whisper Models:
   - Licensed under MIT License
   - Free for commercial and non-commercial use
   - Attribution to OpenAI required

2. Pyannote Speaker Diarization Models:
   - May require accepting specific terms on Hugging Face
   - Some models may have commercial use restrictions
   - Users must obtain appropriate licenses before use

3. Hugging Face Transformers Models:
   - Each model has individual licensing terms
   - Check model cards on Hugging Face Hub before use
   - Some models may restrict commercial usage

Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with all model licenses and
terms of use. This software provides tools to use these models but does not
grant rights to the models themselves.

